name: Expovision Roller Banner
description:
Roller banners have always been one of the most popular promotional materials available, and the Expovision is our most popular product within this range.

This lightweight roller banner is our value option and is perfect for any trade show or exhibition event.

  • Available in 4 different widths: 850mm, 1000mm, 1200mm and 1500mm
  • Standard height of 2000mm across all widths
  • 2 twist out feet add stability
  • Compact lightweight base
  • Single sided banner
  • Includes a Carry Case

name: Bannerbow Arch Expo & Event
description:
Whether you are participating in a roadshow or a event, Bannerbow products can inject that little bit of extra flair you are looking for. The event arches are flexible and can easily be moved from an entrance to an exhibition stand. One product which offers many possibilities.

Our event arches are perfect for exhibitions or as a flexible part of an interior. Our first new product in 2018, Bannerbow Backdrop offers a perfect set for exhibitions and events.

  • Frame Material-fiberglass
  • Foot material - Indoor Aluminium Base or Outdoor Steel Base
  • Printed on 115gsm Knitted Polyester
  • Colour of base - black
  • Depth - 1000mm
  • Transport trolley bag included
  • Indoor or Outdoor use

name: Blizzard Banner
description:
The Blizzard is a firm favourite with outdoor exhibitors that love the way it stands up to the elements, although it is equally at home with indoor exhibitors that want a rugged display that can be used over and over again.

It can withstand 10mph winds when used in conjunction with a PVC banner or up to 18mph winds with mesh material, when the hollow base is filled with sand. That's more than enough for most exhibitions and means you can focus on your work, rather than holding the stand together.Â 

The stand is quick to erect, there are no tools required and the graphic attaches with a simple eyelet system. The Blizzard can support a flag of 800mm x 2000mm, which is enough to get your message across in the busiest exhibition venue or even in a field.

  • Blizzard is ideal for all kinds of corporate and sporting and outdoor events and promotions and point of sale.Â 
  • Its simple design makes it very easy to assemble on-site, and because
  • it's adjustable, it can accommodate different graphic sizes to suit your application.
  • Stylish design hollow plastic base for water or sand weighting agent
  • Base holds 15 litres water approx
  • Telescopic pole for adjustable height
  • Weather resistant
  • Optional carry bag
  • Withstands winds up to 13-18mph approx
  • Size: 800mm (w) x 2000mm (h)
  • Choose from display fabric polyester
  • material or PVC banner material*
  • (*PVC banner material at additional cost)
